cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DL 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper focuses on improving the performance of Resnet on CIFAR-10 and CIFAR-100 datasets, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes an upgraded architecture for Resnet using Squeeze-and-Excitation (SE) block, which is a machine learning technique. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with improving the performance of deep neural networks, which is a core area of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper proposes an architecture that enhances the contribution of bridge-connections in Resnet, which is a type of neural network. 
5. cs.DL (Deep Learning) - The paper deals with improving the performance of deep neural networks, which is a core area of deep learning.
